<dl id="n40173g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40173g">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40173g"> 173(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> apply linen / to demoniacs </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Linen, with its lily-white purity, is the <i>signum</i> of Christ&apos;s burial and resurrection and the predominant fabric of the gospels.</mm> </dd></dl>
